Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.52,0:00:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已经卖完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:14.24,MSE_B,,0,0,0,,{\fn@微软雅黑\fs80\frz270\pos(1076,304)}软绵绵布丁\N{\c&H5345E3&}\h         售完
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}给七七七小姐买礼物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.44,0:00:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的 明天早上我再去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.09,0:00:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看来你打工顺利的完成了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.79,0:00:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有 结果算是白干活了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.40,0:00:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是勉强还是挤出了水电费和七七七的布丁费
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等久了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有问题 时间刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.43,0:00:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是三年级的徒然影虎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.26,0:00:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起我之前偷袭你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.64,0:00:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事 我没有介意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被唯我部长打的伤重多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.66,0:00:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我大冒险部的人都齐了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:29.83,Tittle,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,500)\pos(470,861)}去温泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.21,0:02:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我叫桧野由美 这位是岬鸥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.19,0:02:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是位新人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是岬 请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}由美小姐这次您帮了大忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪里哪里 你们请慢慢休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个 徒然学长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.36,0:02:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}干什么 八真学弟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.34,0:02:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}桧野和唯我部长是什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.12,0:02:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}算是熟人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}顺便说一心的熟人用两手两脚的指头都数不过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原来还有这种特殊技能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:03:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一心早晚会遭报应的 话说快遭报应 给老子遭报应吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小雪 快来快来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里的温泉好像会让皮肤变得滑嫩嫩的哦 好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来 这是三位女生的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个 我是男生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不用介意 这就是这家伙的原梗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天灾好过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}赶快进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}茨学姐 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}唯我部长 我有件事想找你商量一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.52,0:03:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的鼻鼾很严重的 睡觉的时候能让我睡别的房间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了 我去问问老板娘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.78,0:03:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好过分对吧 是个最差劲的大恶人对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}重护那个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:04:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过啊 要是不付水电费的话重护可是会被赶出去的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那稍微拖一会又不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我从战场那吃了大亏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以现在是付不了钱就要立马搬出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这我是能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那实际上怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这次的同屋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过他还是给我买布丁的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么今天就好好的为明天养好神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}星野学妹你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你从刚才就很在意你自己的筷子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有 没有这种事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你没有必要撒这种谎哦 星野学妹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.22,0:05:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就坦率一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你很在意你主人唾液的味道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}达鲁克 原来你在想这种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我没有想过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有必要隐藏的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.79,0:05:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来吧 从你那淫荡的口中伸出你的舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后从下往上舔着品尝…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来 一心大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个…啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被发现的「遗址」就在这个别墅内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}离这里很近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}凭什么判断这里是「遗址」的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.56,0:06:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里的所有人是不存在的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也没有人出入的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.89,0:06:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后 影虎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有问题 周围既没有陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且用你准备的钥匙把大门打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有钥匙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在调查别墅的时候找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}徒然学长 你没有进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 被一心叫停的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}单独去挑战是很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是别墅的略图
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一共两层 而且相当大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天我们兵分两路去寻找「遗址」的入口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个房间很可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}光看这图就能发现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一楼有的柱子在二楼却没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果不是设计问题的话 这应该是有什么缘由的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这你都注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好能干啊 小个子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好厉害啊 天灾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.64,0:07:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 那么我们首先就去看看这个房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天早上我们十点在大厅集合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.28,0:07:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别迟到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们再去泡一次温泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小雪的熟人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的 我和雪姬姐沉浸在肉体的快乐之中…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 是完全不认识的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.51,0:07:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们走吧 静香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小雪 这没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有什么没事的 这跟我没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了重护
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被那个女人置之不理不开心了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是那个时候在升天大楼里那个假女警吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和你的老家有关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么在这个节骨眼上 会出现在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鬼才知道 只是来旅游的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要只是这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天灾胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}重护
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请帮我寄今天到的快递
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.99,0:09:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的 已经接受了委托
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看起来很困嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.17,0:09:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我在办速冻快递的手续 这可是限量的布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是给七七七的礼物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可厉害了 早上6点开店之前就已经有人在排队了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 我先去小睡一会儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}集合时间是10点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}唯我部长他们呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}诶？还没来么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一心君他们的话很早之前就出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又被唯我学长抢先了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个人真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}唯我部长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在下无地自容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要一面对七七七Collection
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总是会想把它据为己有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}于是 遗迹里面什么样子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我觉得是个适合八真君的遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}石柱上有会动的机关
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果找不到正确的路线就会掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}面前的水温和洗澡水差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过越往里面走水温就越高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总而言之 给我上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}诶！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}星野学妹 好绅士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一心大人 我很有事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夕的话就不用我担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.93,0:12:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}相当单纯的机关呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看来没有我出马的必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那家伙是不是得寸进尺了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人尽其才嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这次就让影虎表现一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就交给我吧 不会再出现刚才一样的失态了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.51,0:12:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我总是依赖着大家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太天真了 什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没啥大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:12:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天灾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天灾 不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我倒是没什么 不过重护啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好像很熟悉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是偶然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让我上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在这里掉下去的话可不是闹着玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我不行的话 接下来就麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么我走左边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.19,0:13:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}脱光了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不是说了我先上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知不觉就上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.37,0:14:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个是七七七Collection？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先休息一下再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:15:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}八真君 这之后我想去问七七七一点事情 可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 我想七七七一定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}徒然学长 你的肌肉好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}八真学弟也相当不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一心也稍微锻炼一下怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手腕这么细
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别摸我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.31,0:15:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一心大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}水温真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.44,0:15:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的话还是要再热一点比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别逞强了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 等等 你碰到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}茨殿下 偷窥是犯罪哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只是在守望自己心爱之人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一心大人 为什么不看这里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}二年级的给我滚开 杀了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您慢用…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么我就先出去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}八真 把脸凑过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亲~亲~亲~天灾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好热
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}七七七Collection 不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.82,0:16:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 我们泡温泉的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}由美小姐和岬小姐在打扫是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老板娘在服务台整理账本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}达库克君在房间里泡澡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}静香小姐在房间里休息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不义小姐在游戏场玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:16:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是没看到可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.05,0:17:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.44,0:17:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}话说只要考虑下情况就知道犯人是你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下啊 虽然小雪不太搭理人很难交往
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但不是那种会偷人东西的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.94,0:17:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雪姬姐不是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然你们都说到这份上了 我想听一下你们的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你去哪里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了证明自己的推理的正确
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把除此以外的可能性全给舍弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}犯人就在这些人之中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有几个问题要问不义殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}重护你们三人以外 还有谁从那间更衣室里进出了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.77,0:17:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}唉？那…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天灾 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这的确是遗迹里找到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}达鲁克 你在哪找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}压在要洗的衣服堆里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}进入男澡堂也不会被当成可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为是服务员 是吧 不义殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.31,0:18:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最后的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个服务员是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.06,0:18:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是那边的服务员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是说犯人就是你 岬鸥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.49,0:18:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我没有理由偷这个布偶啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.29,0:18:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不用解释了 怪盗百相脸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}话说为什么会被看穿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.38,0:18:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没想到真的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.11,0:18:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}胡乱猜的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管怎么说算是失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.39,0:18:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老板娘 作为打工费就给真正的小岬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:18:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毕竟是我擅自冒充了她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}影虎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.60,0:19:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用追了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.47,0:19:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.44,0:19:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}干什么啊 名侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.46,0:19:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是打算和那两个人联手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后去入手七七七Collection的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让我觉得奇怪的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你明明打工失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}却跟房东付了水电费
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你把遗迹的情报透漏给「祭」换到了钱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原来如此 然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让「祭」的两人去旅馆待命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们拿到七七七Collection后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找好机会就偷出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个叫不义雪姬的女人只是诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家都抱着怀疑的眼光看过来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:20:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}百面相就去回收了七七七Collection的打算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是了不起的推理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你为什么没有在那时候说出我和「祭」的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为没有实质上的证据吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后这个数据 下次就会成为我的优势
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.49,0:20:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以假装猜对了岬鸥的真实身份吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.06,0:20:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还真是厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对手啊 被你看穿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这一般都是坏人说的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}唯我君 这不是七七七Collection哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.14,0:20:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下 这个布偶的确是在「遗址」的宝箱里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是我不认识这东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是说 是假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很早之前就已经有人把七七七Collection拿走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.34,0:20:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宝箱里的东西就是假的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在生气…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快点来啊
